Hello and a hell of a good morning (*THANKS TO YOUR MUSIC*) ^_^  to you all :3 hi hi ummmm well guess im not sure if you guys will read this but hope you do lol im not going to say im a big fan of yours because i feel like you get that alot :D but i am ^_^ehem anyway XD ........ Just passing by to say guys keep doing an awesome job with your music videos and everything you guys are one of the few artist i love because your music has that surtin feeling in it, it has that vibe that makes you want to do something about yourself im not saying this because im a kiss up but you guys do a pretty damn good job with your lyrics =D keep up the awesome work guys ♥ :3 I actually made my own lyrics and they have a same surtin feeling as this song and the monster song is one of my favs to im not sure but your music has alot of sense in it for thoughs who understand i believe theyve been through somethings similar i guess im not sure lol im not sure of many things but im sure that i love your music guys!!!!!
